Class PermissionResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.amelia.permissions.PermissionResult

  • public class PermissionResult
extends java.lang.Object
    Holds the union between Permission and PermissibleEntity
    Also provides access to assign(References) and assign(VoluntaryBoolean, References)
